--====================================================================
--  VISUAL TRADE SPAWNER  --  LocalScript (client-side only)
--====================================================================
--  Put this in a LocalScript (e.g. StarterPlayer > StarterPlayerScripts).
--
--  This is PURELY VISUAL. It only edits GUI on the client running it.
--  Nothing here is replicated to the server or to other players, so it
--  cannot change another player's screen, trade, or inventory.
--
--  All executor-only functions from the old version were removed:
--    * getconnections / firing other scripts' signals  -> GONE
--    * :Activate() spoof-clicking the real trade button -> GONE
--    * readfile / isfile / writefile (file saving)      -> GONE
--    * setclipboard (website copy)                       -> GONE
--    * the whole auto-accept system that read the OTHER  -> GONE
--      player's ReadyButton / ACCEPT state
--  None of those work in a normal LocalScript anyway.
--====================================================================

